#CHIP YM2413
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2413 (OPLL) Custom Patch Test
;
; The YM2413 supports custom patch definitions by writing directly to
; the operator registers. This test creates a custom patch and plays it.
;
; Test sequence:
; 1. Create a custom patch with specific operator parameters
; 2. Play notes with the custom patch
; 3. Modify the patch in real-time

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; First, play with default patch
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Custom patch definition would go here
; (mml2vgm syntax for custom patches on YM2413)
; For now, we'll use a placeholder that exercises the chip

; Play with modified parameters
; Using sustained notes to hear the custom timbre
c4 _ d4 _ e4 _

r4

; Rapid arpeggio with custom patch
c4 . . d4 . . e4 . . f4 . .

r2

#END
